(Translated by Google) Beautiful resort I love the architecture. Clean and very practical in the summer to go all around. I work around the clock and it's easy to get there thanks to this station.

(Original)
Belle station j’adore l’architecture. Propre et très pratique l’été pour aller à la ronde. Je travail à la ronde et c’est facile de m’y rendre grâce à cette station.

(Translated by Google) Large and renovated. ☺

(Original)
Vaste et rénové. ☺

(Translated by Google) Very nice resort

(Original)
Très belle station
